NAME
    Catalyst::Model::WebService::Solr - Use WebService::Solr in your
    Catalyst application

SYNOPSIS
        package MyApp::Model::Solr;
    
        use base qw( Catalyst::Model::WebService::Solr );
    
        __PACKAGE__->config(
            server  => 'http://localhost:8080/solr/',
            options => {
                autocommit => 1,
            }
        );

DESCRIPTION
    This module helps you use remote indexes via WebService::Solr in your
    Catalyst application.

METHODS
  COMPONENT( )
    passes your config options to WebService::Solr's "new" method.

SEE ALSO
    * Catalyst
    * WebService::Solr

